in_n_out_url <- "https://www.lasvegas360.com/3428/in-n-out-burger-locations-and-store-numbers/"
in_n_out_link <- read_html(in_n_out_url)

establishment_html <- html_nodes(in_n_out_link, css = "table")
establishment_text <- html_table(establishment_html, fill = T)
# 1b
data1 <- establishment_text[1]
data1 <- as.data.frame(data1)
data2 <- establishment_text[2]
data2 <- as.data.frame(data2)
names(data1) <- c("Observation Number", "Photo", "City", "Address", "State", "Open Date")
data1 <- data1[ , -c(2)]
names(data2) <- c("Observation Number", "City", "Address", "State", "Open Date")
data2 <- data2[-c(1), ]

in_n_out_data <- rbind(data1, data2)
#1c
in_n_out_data[5,4] <- "CA"
in_n_out_data[5,5] <- "10/5/1959"
#1d

for (i in 1:333) {
    for (j in 1:50) {
        if (state.abb[j] == in_n_out_data[i,4]) {
           in_n_out_data[i,6] <- state.name[j]
        }
    }
}

names(in_n_out_data)[6] <- "Full State Name"
#1e
ggplot(data = in_n_out_data, aes(x = `Full State Name`, col = `Full State Name`, fill = `Full State Name`)) + geom_bar()

#2a
dd_url <- "https://www.menuism.com/restaurant-locations/dunkin-donuts-181624/us"
dd_link <- read_html(dd_url)
dd_html <- html_nodes(dd_link, css = ".list-unstyled-links a")
dd_text <- html_text(dd_html)


sb_url <- "https://www.menuism.com/restaurant-locations/starbucks-coffee-39564/us"
sb_link <- read_html(sb_url)
sb_html <- html_nodes(sb_link, css = ".list-unstyled-links a")
sb_text <- html_text(sb_html)
#2b

dd_text <- str_replace(dd_text, "Dunkin' Donuts locations", " ")
dd_text <- str_replace(dd_text, "\\(", "         ")
dd_text <- str_replace(dd_text, "\\)", "")

dd_state <- as.data.frame(str_sub(dd_text, 1 , -14))
dd_count <- as.data.frame(str_sub(dd_text, -4, -1))

dd_data <- cbind(dd_state, dd_count)
names(dd_data) <- c("State", "Number of Dunkin' Donuts")


sb_text <- str_replace(sb_text, "Starbucks Coffee locations", " ")
sb_text <- str_replace(sb_text, "\\(", "         ")
sb_text <- str_replace(sb_text, "\\)", "")

sb_state <- as.data.frame(str_sub(sb_text, 1, -8))
sb_count <- as.data.frame(str_sub(sb_text, -5, -1))

sb_data <- cbind(sb_state, sb_count)
names(sb_data) <- c("State", "Number of Starbucks")

sb_data[,1] <- str_trim(sb_data[,1], "right")
sb_data[,1] <- str_to_lower(sb_data[,1])
sb_data[,1] <- as.character(sb_data[,1])
sb_data[,2] <- str_trim(sb_data[,2], "left")
sb_data[,2] <- as.numeric(sb_data[,2])
dd_data[,1] <- str_trim(dd_data[,1], "right")
dd_data[,1] <- str_to_lower(dd_data[,1])
dd_data[,1] <- as.character(dd_data[,1])
dd_data[,2] <- str_trim(dd_data[,2], "left")
dd_data[,2] <- as.numeric(dd_data[,2])
#2c

all_data <- merge(sb_data, dd_data, by = "State", all = T)
all_data$`Number of Dunkin' Donuts`[is.na(all_data$`Number of Dunkin' Donuts`)] <- 0


for (i in 1:51) {
    if (all_data$`Number of Starbucks`[i] > all_data$`Number of Dunkin' Donuts`[i]) {
        all_data[i,4] <- "darkgreen"
    } else {
        all_data[i,4] <- "deeppink"
    }
}

names(all_data)[4] <- "Color"
#2d
a <- map("state", plot = F)
statenames <- as.character(a$names)
statenames <- as.data.frame(statenames)


for (i in 1:length(statenames[,1])) {
    for (j in 1:length(all_data[,1])) {
        if (statenames[i,1] == all_data[j,1]) {
           statenames[i,2] <- all_data[j,2]
           statenames[i,3] <- all_data[j,3]
           statenames[i,4] <- all_data[j,4]
        }
    }
}

names(statenames)[2] <- "Number of Starbucks"
names(statenames)[3] <- "Number of Dunkin' Donuts"
names(statenames)[4] <- "Color"


statenames[20,4] <- all_data[22,4]
statenames[21,4] <- all_data[22,4]
statenames[22,4] <- all_data[22,4]
statenames[23,4] <- all_data[23,4]
statenames[24,4] <- all_data[23,4]
statenames[34,4] <- all_data[33,4]
statenames[35,4] <- all_data[33,4]
statenames[36,4] <- all_data[33,4]
statenames[37,4] <- all_data[33,4]
statenames[38,4] <- all_data[34,4]
statenames[39,4] <- all_data[34,4]
statenames[40,4] <- all_data[34,4]
statenames[53,4] <- all_data[47,4]
statenames[54,4] <- all_data[47,4]
statenames[55,4] <- all_data[47,4]
statenames[56,4] <- all_data[48,4]
statenames[57,4] <- all_data[48,4]
statenames[58,4] <- all_data[48,4]
statenames[59,4] <- all_data[48,4]
statenames[60,4] <- all_data[48,4]


map("state", regions = all_data$State, fill = T, col = statenames$Color) 
title(main = "Dunkin Donuts vs Starbucks") 
legend("bottomleft", legend = c("Starbucks", "Dunkin' Donuts"), pch = 16, col = unique(statenames$Color))
